  "help": [
    {
      "textLabel": "This tool calculates the rate of return you'll need with the new investment in order to justify selling today and paying taxes and transaction fees."
    },
    {
      "textLabel": "You may be tempted to sell stock you now own if you believe another investment will provide a higher rate of return. However, if you sell, you may incur transaction fees and income taxes that reduce both your return and the amount available for the new investment. Additionally, you may incur more fees with the new investment."
    }
  ],
